# PyVerify Test Automation Framework

[![Supported versions](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9%20%7C%203.10%20%7C%203.11%20%7C%203.12-blue)](https://gitlab.intra.infineon.com/global_projects/PyVerify-Ecosystem/ecosystem/ifx-pyverify)
[![CI](https://gitlab.intra.infineon.com/global_projects/PyVerify-Ecosystem/ecosystem/ifx-pyverify/badges/main/pipeline.svg?ignore_skipped=true)](https://gitlab.intra.infineon.com/global_projects/PyVerify-Ecosystem/ecosystem/ifx-pyverify/-/pipelines?page=1&scope=all&ref=main)
